<p>In this rat race world we live in nowadays, all we need is to be always on the go but the need to fill
ourselves with satisfying meals at the same time would be a real challenge. But Rice in a box is here to
provide just what we need, meal to go in an instant! The company started way back in year 2000 in Manila's
Chinatown. It specializes in authentic Chinese dishes served in a box to go.

The rice meal is being served in a convenient small box people can have their meal even they are mobile,
how convenient could that get? The food it serves is prepared right upon order in front of the customers
so that it is ensured that it always clean, hot, fresh and good quality. What better way to enjoy a satisfying
meal than that? Another good thing, the meals are very affordable it caters all target market even the masses
could afford! Aside from rice meals, it also offers noodles and rice toppings too
